  "id": "RAW_36f78930",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-17）：微软开源 3D 生成模型 TRELLIS.2， 凭 40 亿参数基座实现高保真 PBR 材质 3D 资产生成",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500937&idx=1&sn=5dee235ba08c513927d59fc0604cf298",
  "date": "2025-12-17 09:53:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：TRELLIS.2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"410\" data-imgfileid=\"100017272\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe4a401e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRhwqWGKzIwBoMNtBVyuNOrCViafBiaotHktegWaF4F3FeUofUV2yjZCwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★TRELLIS.2 是一个先进的3D生成模型，专为高保真图像到3D生成而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它采用了一种新颖的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">“无场”稀疏体素结构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，称为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">O-Voxel</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，以及一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">大规模的流匹配Transformer</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">（拥有40亿参数）。与依赖于等值面场的方法不同，TRELLIS能够重建和生成具有复杂拓扑、锐利特征和完整物理基础渲染材料的任意3D资产。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trellis-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trellis-2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：HY-WorldPlay</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"558\" data-imgfileid=\"100017274\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=615f8e87&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRl75vfxylvEeuEGqiatnQhZCiatv9LT0hKuNrXLKzqNgOeic0Nzl5N3oag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★HY-WorldPlay是一个用于实时交互世界建模的系统框架，能够在保持几何一致性的同时实现实时生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过四个关键设计实现了这一目标，包括</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">双重动作表示、重构上下文记忆、WorldCompass增强学习框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">上下文强制蒸馏方法</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。HY-World 1.5能够以24 FPS的速度生成长时间的视频流，支持多种场景和视角，适用于3D重建、事件提示和无限世界扩展等应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hy-worldplay\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hy-worldplay</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：VGGT4D</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"100017273\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7fbd6fe2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRa8VepmuCkhJ96vibhqFwnyYO6AjoKR9zLORsvC9Rh9Y1Fy5Yfp6ajAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★VGGT4D项目是一个基于视觉几何变换器的4D场景重建工具，旨在通过挖掘运动线索来提升场景重建的精度。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了官方实现，支持用户在自己的数据上运行模型，生成深度图、相机内参、相机位姿等输出。项目依托于香港科技大学（广州）和Horizon Robotics的研究成果，适用于需要高精度动态场景重建的科研和应用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vggt-4-d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vggt-4-d</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：LongCat-Video-Avatar</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"302\" data-imgfileid=\"100017270\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d45cbf88&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRA2eFcpLNyJ4gayN3PZ9RefahevPPiapMjCEKqMoYd2KFeqmzX0kkdtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Long</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Cat-Video-Avatar 是一个统一的模型，能够实现富有表现力和高度动态的音频驱动角色动画</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该模型支持多种生成模式，包括</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">音频-文本到视频、音频-图像-文本到视频</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以及</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视频延续</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。其设计旨在通过解耦语音信号与运动动态，实现自然的人类行为表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/longcatvideo-avatar\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/longcatvideo-avatar</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LiteGS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35555555555555557\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"414\" data-imgfileid=\"100017276\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c352f117&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRIax5EUJ6XeGibQZSqpPx5RDYhoeCVMaicAwC7f5EVC0Y91qW6W4OpibDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LiteGS是一个经过重构的代码库，旨在提高高斯散点技术的灵活性和性能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目能够在大约50秒内完成3D高斯散点的训练。LiteGS提供了纯Python和CUDA两种实现方式，支持快速原型开发和性能优化。其模块化设计允许更容易地访问中间变量，并通过PyTorch Autograd减少手动推导梯度公式的需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/litegs\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/litegs</a> &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MemVerse</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.287962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"336\" data-imgfileid=\"100017275\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d84d18c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxLIhvCaooXnfXvWwpbDuYRA6lW0hu2K0FgfCKZeBknD4gItd1exup7ZiaoxwywR64RTmbpA9vVtug%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MemVerse是一个开源框架，旨在为AI Agent提供连续的多模态记忆。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">组织和检索文本、图像</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">及</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">其他感官输入的信息</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，使Agent能够记住过去的互动、理解上下文并动态适应。MemVerse通过将</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">记忆结构化为分层知识图谱</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并结合快速参数化回忆，赋予AI推理、互动和在扩展对话中提供连贯</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">、个性化体验的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mem-verse\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mem-verse</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了微软 TRELLIS.2 等六个近期开源项目，涵盖高保真 3D 生成、实时世界建模、4D 场景重建、音视频角色动画、高性能高斯散点代码库以及多模态 AI Agent 记忆框架。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了微软 TRELLIS.2 等六个近期开源项目，涵盖高保真 3D 生成、实时世界建模、4D 场景重建、音视频角色动画、高性能高斯散点代码库以及多模态 AI Agent 记忆框架。",
